*xdm-0.99.2_p20051026-r2 (02 Nov 2005)

  02 Nov 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  +xdm-0.99.2_p20051026-r2.ebuild:
  Install Xsession to /usr/libdir, not /etc, so we don't get 2 copies of it.

